! scope="row"|费尔斯堂<br><small>（Firth Court）</small>
|[[File:Firth_Court,_Sheffield_University.jpg|120px]]
|align="center" |1905
|align="center" |二級
|费尔斯堂是大學的主要行政中心。創校時文理醫三學院共用此樓，目前則由分子生物學和生物技術，以及生物醫學科學學系進駐。费尔斯堂由艾華·米謝爾·吉布斯（Edward Mitchel Gibbs）以垂直式復興風格設計<ref name="List Entry">{{cite web |url=https://historicengland.org.uk/listing/the-list/list-entry/1247504 |title=EDGAR ALLEN BUILDING, FIRTH HALL, ROTUNDA AND QUADRANGLE |year=1995 |accessdate=17 August 2020 |publisher=Historic England}}</ref>，於1903至1905年間建造<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.architecture.com/image-library/RIBApix/image-information/poster/new-university-building-abutting-firth-court-western-bank-university-of-sheffield-the-entrance-appro/posterid/RIBA63245.html |title=New university building abutting Firth Court |year=2020 |accessdate=17 August 2020 |publisher=Royal Institute of British Architects}}</ref> ，並以馬克·费尔斯命名<ref name="Historical note"/>。大樓在1905年由英王愛德華七世及亞歷山德拉皇后開幕。费尔斯堂方庭由主樓、北座、西座和弗洛里樓組成；吉布斯原先計劃在建築群內建造雙庭，惟此未見穷期<ref name="List Entry"/>。方庭曾於二戰期間用作防空洞<ref name="Historical note"/>。
|-
! scope="row"|费尔斯堂圓樓<br><small>（The Rotunda）</small>
|[[File:University_of_Sheffield_Rotunda_(geograph_3208097).jpg|120px]]
|align="center" |1909
|align="center" |二級
|新哥特式圓樓為位於费尔斯堂左側的[[巨筒|巨筒]]，頂部帶金字塔形玻璃尖頂，內部為圓形拱廊<ref name="List Entry"/>。圓樓與费尔斯堂主樓以玻璃走廊連接。大樓的前身是在1909年4月26日由[[威爾斯親王|威爾斯親王]]和[[威爾斯王妃|王妃]]所啟用的埃德加·艾倫圖書館（Edgar Allen Library）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.picturesheffield.com/frontend.php?keywords=Ref_No_increment;EQUALS;s06636&pos=2&action=zoom |title=University of Sheffield and Edgar Allen Library |year=2015 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |publisher=Picture Sheffield |archive-date=2015-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118231550/http://www.picturesheffield.com/frontend.php?keywords=Ref_No_increment;EQUALS;s06636&pos=2&action=zoom |dead-url=no }}</ref>，目前為書記官及秘書處<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sheffield.ac.uk/polopoly_fs/1.432134!/file/campus-map-dec2014-3000.gif |title=University of Sheffield Map |year=2015 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |publisher=University of Sheffield |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924122254/http://www.sheffield.ac.uk/polopoly_fs/1.432134!/file/campus-map-dec2014-3000.gif |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
|-
! scope="row"|維畔圖書館<br><small>（Western Bank Library）</small>
|[[File:Western_Bank_Library,_The_Arts_Tower_Complex,_Winter_Street,_Sheffield_(geograph_3782210).jpg|120px]]
|align="center" |1959
|align="center" |二*級
|圖書館是英國二*級[[登錄建築|登錄建築]]。曾名為大學圖書館（University Library），直至資訊館啟用前都是谢菲尔德大学的主圖書館。維士敦畔圖書館館藏25,000冊古籍善本和150冊特殊藏書<ref>[[English_Heritage|English Heritage]] (1993) [http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/details/default.aspx?pid=2&id=457011 Library and Arts Tower, University of Sheffield.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/details/default.aspx?pid=2&id=457011 |date=20170319221012 }} ''Images of England'' (accessed 7 January 2006—free registration required).</ref>。
|-
! scope="row"|[[文塔_(英國)|文塔]]<br><small>（Arts Tower）</small>
|[[File:Arts_Tower_S_2013.jpg|120px]]
|align="center" |1966
|align="center" |二*級
|文塔是二*級登錄建築，建於1966年，由[[伊莉莎白王太后|伊莉莎白王太后]]揭幕<ref name="MATHERS">Mathers, H. (2005) ''Steel City Scholars, The Centenary History of the University of Sheffield'', p191. James and James (Publishers) Ltd. ISBN 1-904022-01-4</ref>。[[英格蘭遺產委員會|英格蘭遺產委員會]]稱之為「該時期最優雅的英國大學高樓建築」（the most elegant university tower block in Britain of its period）<ref>[http://www.thestar.co.uk/news/Multimillion-pound-revamp-for-city.3748289.jp Multimillion pound revamp for city structure] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/news/Multimillion-pound-revamp-for-city.3748289.jp |date=20080207120622 }} - ''Sheffield Star'' 6 February 2008</ref>。文塔樓高78米、共20層，在1965年至2010年是谢菲尔德市最高的建築物，目前仍是全英國最高的大學建築物<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.worldarchitecturenews.com/index.php?fuseaction=wanappln.projectview&upload_id=170 |title=World Architecture News |accessdate=2020-09-12 |archive-date=2012-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210083901/http://www.worldarchitecturenews.com/index.php?fuseaction=wanappln.projectview&upload_id=170 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Campus landmarks"/>。大樓因原為文學系（arts departments）主樓而命名為文塔（Arts Tower）<ref name="MATHERS"/>；現則為建築學院、景觀設計學系及大學行政中心。文塔與維畔圖書館以行人天橋相連<ref name="PEVSNER">Harman, R. & Minnis, J. (2004) ''Pevsner City Guides: Sheffield'', pp82–84. New Haven & London: Yale University Press. ISBN 0-300-10585-1</ref>。文塔擁有歐洲僅有現仍運作的链斗式升降機。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flemming-hamburg.de/patlist.htm#grossbritannien|title=PatList|publisher=|accessdate=16 July 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213160407/http://www.flemming-hamburg.de/patlist.htm#grossbritannien|archive-date=2017-02-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
|-
! scope="row"|大學樓<br><small>（University House）</small>
|[[File:Shefunistudentunion2012.JPG|120px]]
|align="center" |1963
|align="center" |無
|大學樓1963年落成，是世界最早的玻璃[[幕牆|幕牆]]建築之一。<ref name=BBCRefurb>{{cite news|title=University of Sheffield 'pioneering' building in £20m revamp|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-18121332|accessdate=28 December 2013|newspaper=BBC News Online|date=19 May 2012|archive-date=2012-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522145217/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-18121332|dead-url=no}}</ref>建築群在2012至13年間重新設計及翻新，現為谢菲尔德學生會大樓<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/news/nr/university-house-students-union-refurbishment-1.179416 |title=Multi-million pound refurbishment to bring pioneering building into the 21st century |publisher=University of Sheffield |accessdate=19 August 2020 |archive-date=2016-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318213732/http://www.sheffield.ac.uk/news/nr/university-house-students-union-refurbishment-1.179416 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
