! scope="row"|馬平樓<br><small>（Sir Frederick Mappin Building）</small>
|[[File:Sir_Frederick_Mappin_Building.jpg|120px]]
|align="center" |1885
|align="center" |二級
|馬平樓為二級登錄建築，是工程學院的主建築<ref name="Campus landmarks">{{cite web |url=https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/visitors/landmarks |title=Campus landmarks |publisher=University of Sheffield |accessdate=24 June 2015 |archive-date=2016-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105195058/https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/visitors/landmarks |dead-url=no }}</ref>。馬平樓內最古老的部份名為中央翼，1885年竣工，前身是谢菲尔德技術學院大樓。2020年初，大學翻新馬平樓和中央翼，並在兩棟建築物之間加建弧形玻璃天幕<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.scci.org.uk/news/universitys-engineering-heartspace-wins-distinguished-award-for-social-impact/ | title=University's Engineering Heartspace wins distinguished award for social impact |publisher=Royal Institute of Chartered Surveyors | accessdate=18 August 2020}}</ref>，中庭另設實驗室、辦公室及社交空間<ref name="Engineering campus">{{cite web |url=https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/engineering/campus |title=Engineering campus |website=www.architecture.com |publisher=University of Sheffield |accessdate=19 August 2020 |archive-date=2020-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510104050/https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/engineering/campus |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

