! scope="row"|積索樓<br><small>（Jessop Building）</small>
|[[File:Jessop_Hospital_2011.jpg|120px]]
|align="center" |1878
|align="center" |二級
|積索樓前身為積索婦女醫院，1878年7月22日由湯瑪斯·積索捐款創辦。醫院2001年停業，大樓由谢菲尔德大學接管<ref name=NHS>{{cite web|url=http://www.sth.nhs.uk/our-hospitals/jessop-wing|publisher=Sheffield Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust|title=Jessop Wing|accessdate=22 October 2018|archive-date=2019-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531163013/https://www.sth.nhs.uk/our-hospitals/jessop-wing|dead-url=no}}</ref>。積索樓原由[[維多利亞時代|維多利亞]]翼、[[愛德華時代|愛德華]]翼和[[1970年代|七十年代]]翼組成。大學在2007年展開大型发展計劃，同年拆除七十年代翼；<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/southyorkshire/content/image_galleries/jessops_hospital_old_gallery.shtml|publisher=BBC|title=Goodbye Jessop Hospital|accessdate=22 October 2018|archive-date=2015-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429000034/http://www.bbc.co.uk/southyorkshire/content/image_galleries/jessops_hospital_old_gallery.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年維多利亞翼改作音乐系大樓<ref name=Music>{{cite web|url=https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/music/facilities/jessop-building|title=Jessop Building|publisher=University of Sheffield|accessdate=22 October 2018|archive-date=2018-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022193532/https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/music/facilities/jessop-building|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然愛德華翼是二級登錄建築，大學仍在2013年決定將之清拆重建<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-21955502|title=Sheffield Jessop Hospital wing demolition approved|date=27 March 2013|publisher=BBC|accessdate=22 October 2018|archive-date=2020-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224215330/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-21955502|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以建造更大型的教學樓（即谢菲尔德鑽石）<ref name= ShefTelegraph>{{cite web|url=http://www.sheffieldtelegraph.co.uk/news/local/university-gears-up-with-134m-expansion-scheme-1-4469773|work=Sheffield Telegraph|date=22 April 2012|title=University gears up with £134m expansion scheme|accessdate=22 October 2018|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002016/http://www.sheffieldtelegraph.co.uk/news/local/university-gears-up-with-134m-expansion-scheme-1-4469773|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
